{"title":"现代文阅读方法","uid":"00a0d969d005e26a70950b90b964790c","slug":"现代文阅读方法","date":"2022-05-24T13:37:36.000Z","updated":"2022-05-24T13:38:05.467Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/现代文阅读方法.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"现代文阅读方法\">现代文阅读方法</h1>\r\n<h3 id=\"一-基本步骤\">一、 基本步骤</h3>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p>先看文后题目再读文章并圈点勾画</p>\r\n<p>明确用什么知识点回答</p></li>\r\n<li><p>注意审题（包括分值）</p></li>\r\n<li><p>思考文章主要内容与主题</p></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>主题：</p>\r\n<p>通过写...事</p>\r\n<p>表现（达）了...的主题</p></li>\r\n<li><p>内容：</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"二品味赏析语言的角度\">二、品味赏析语言的角度</h3>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p>修辞：</p>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p>比喻：</p>\r\n<p>运用了比喻，</p>\r\n<p>将...比作...，</p>\r\n<p>生动形象地写出了...（物）...的特点，</p>\r\n<p>表达了作者...的思想感情。</p></li>\r\n<li><p>拟人：</p>\r\n<p>运用了拟人，</p>\r\n<p>...（词）将...赋予以人的...，</p>\r\n<p>生动形象地写出了...（物）...的特点，</p>\r\n<p>表达了作者...的思想感情。</p></li>\r\n<li><p>对比：</p>\r\n<p>运用了对比，</p>\r\n<p>将...与...对比，</p>\r\n<p>突出了...（物）...的特点，</p>\r\n<p>表达了作者...的思想感情。</p></li>\r\n</ol></li>\r\n<li><p>描写（目的---表现人物形象）</p>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p>人物描写</p></li>\r\n<li><p>环境描写</p></li>\r\n</ol></li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 id=\"三一段话在文中的作用\">三、一段话在文中的作用</h3>\r\n<p><strong>内容上</strong> ：</p>\r\n<p><strong>结构上</strong> ：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>文首：开门见山、开篇点题、引出下文、总领全文等</li>\r\n<li>文中：承上启下（过渡）、作为线索等</li>\r\n<li>文尾：总结全文、升华了...主题、前后呼应、再次点题、深化主题、点明主题等</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"四文章标题的作用\">四、文章标题的作用</h3>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p>概括了 <strong>文章的主要内容</strong> ： ...</p></li>\r\n<li><p>作为 <strong>线索贯穿全文</strong> ，全文写了...事，\r\n都围绕标题...写.</p></li>\r\n<li><p>点明或暗示了 <strong>文章的主题</strong> ：...</p></li>\r\n<li><p>标题 <strong>新颖</strong> ，吸引读者，激发读者阅读兴趣</p></li>\r\n<li><p>点明了故事发生的 <strong>时间地点环境</strong> 等</p></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 id=\"五文章标题的含义\">五、文章标题的含义</h3>\r\n<p><strong>表面意思</strong> ： <strong>标题的字面含义</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>深层含义</strong> ： <strong>联系文章的中心解答</strong></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>持续更新中...</p>\r\n","text":"现代文阅读方法 一、 基本步骤 先看文后题目再读文章并圈点勾画 明确用什么知识点回答 注意审题（包括分值） 思考文章主要内容与主题 主题： 通过写...事 表现（达）了...的主题 内容： 二、品味赏析语言的角度 修辞： 比喻： 运用了比喻， 将...比作...， 生动形象地写出...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":674,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Chinese","slug":"Chinese","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Chinese.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%87%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">现代文阅读方法</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、 基本步骤</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E5%93%81%E5%91%B3%E8%B5%8F%E6%9E%90%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、品味赏析语言的角度</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E8%AF%9D%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三、一段话在文中的作用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">四、文章标题的作用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%94%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">五、文章标题的含义</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"YingHN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"“有声”的父爱","uid":"f8accd8797811c2077025663b395ce50","slug":"“有声”的父爱","date":"2022-05-26T13:41:00.000Z","updated":"2022-07-08T13:26:30.734Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/“有声”的父爱.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"“有声”的父亲 在军营里，诸葛瞻的父亲写下《诫子书》；在油灯旁，苏洵为儿子教学《战国策》；在水缸边，王羲之与儿子苦练书法 人人的父亲各异，我的父亲是 “有声” 的。 父亲在家里会发出个性的声音。他做完了事，便拖着沉重的步伐行到床前，眼”刷”地一下闭了，四肢如没有骨头一样倒在床上。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":871,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Literature","slug":"Literature","count":9,"path":"api/tags/Literature.json"}],"author":{"name":"YingHN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"MarkDown公式书写","uid":"2929836d59d95692b6043d49510b51db","slug":"MarkDown公式书写","date":"2022-05-23T13:56:54.000Z","updated":"2022-05-23T13:58:11.222Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MarkDown公式书写.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"MarkDown公式书写 一般公式分为两种形式，行内公式和行间公式。 行内公式： 行间公式： 对应的代码块为： $ \\Gamma(z) &#x3D; \\int_0^\\infty t^&#123;z-1&#125;e^&#123;-t&#125;dt\\,. $ $$\\Gamma(z...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"9k","symbolsTime":"8 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"MarkDown","slug":"MarkDown","count":1,"path":"api/tags/MarkDown.json"}],"author":{"name":"YingHN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}